Class Country

java.lang.Object
Country
public class Country extends Object
The Country class gets and sets the Country Name, Capitol, Population, GDP (Gross Domestic Product), Area, and Happiness Index of a Country object. It also contains a method to print a Country object.
Version:
10/05/2023
Author:
Emma Choi
